snippet.title: Winx Club: Magical Fairy Party - DS - Become a fashionable part of the Winx Club!
snippet.description:
Create your own fairy and get ready for the most magical party you have ever been invited to! 
Follow the adventures of your favorite Winx through dozens of mini-games, coming on your Nintendo DS™.
Check out the cool features of the game into this trailer!

Winx Club: Magical Fairy Party is now available on Nintendo DS.
For more information, please visit your local Namco Bandai website, http://www.namcobandaigames.eu

Talk about this game, share tips & win goodies at http://www.namcobandaigames.eu/community
